svg.title: web-design
svg.text: I created front-end UIs, back-end apps and websites using HTML, CSS, JS, Angular, React, WPF, Node.Js, Ruby Rails, MongoDB and PostGreSql. Some examples are a loan service for automating processing applications, global hybrid cloud disaster recovery system, a multi-tenant PaaS/ SaaS networking tool and SEO tools.

I follow an agile design philosophy using sprint based planning and execution, following industry standards and applying object oriented designand analysis for developing websites. My apps work cross-platform on Windows, MacOs/ IOS and Linux/ Unix environments.

I create original artwork for my websites including wireframes, web layouts,templates, icons and scenes for animation. I bring the scenes to life by meticulously animating effects. The end result is a beautiful, pixel-perfect transition that adds a lively flair to the content in bringing creative ideas to life.
I volunteer for non-profitorganizations and consultant for end-clients.
I completed the Web Development Immersivecourse at General Assembly.
